<item>
            <title>[LU-4211] Test failure on test suite sanity-lfsck, subtest test_7b</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4211</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/dc34d5de-4637-11e3-83ac-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/dc34d5de-4637-11e3-83ac-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There appear to be only 2 instances of this specific error recorded in maloo.  The recent one (above) and an old one from 5/15:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c4808f28-bd84-11e2-a548-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c4808f28-bd84-11e2-a548-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_7b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(7) Expect &apos;scanning-phase2&apos;, but got &apos;completed&apos;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity-lfsck 7b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
